headline: CBRE (NYSE:CBRE) Beats Q3 Sales Expectations
summary: Commercial real estate firm CBRE (NYSE:CBRE) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 13.5% year on year to $10.26 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.61 per share was 10.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
